            "explanation": "Softmax formula: $\\text{softmax}(z_i) = \\dfrac{e^{z_i}}{\\sum_j e^{z_j}}$\n\nExponentiate each value: $e^{z} = [1.000,\\ 2.718,\\ 1.278,\\ 1.185,\\ 1.148]$\n\nSum: $1.000 + 2.718 + 1.278 + 1.185 + 1.148 = 7.329$\n\nDivide each value by $7.329$: $\\text{softmax}(z) = [0.136,\\ 0.371,\\ 0.174,\\ 0.162,\\ 0.157]$"
