            "accepted": ["3", "$3$", "y = 3", "y=3"],
            "explanation": "Each internal unit is a linear combination of the inputs plus a bias; the output is the maximum.\n\n$z_1 = 2x_1 + 1 \\cdot x_2 + (-2) = 2(2) + 1 - 2 = 3$\n\n$z_2 = 0 \\cdot x_1 + (-2)x_2 + 2 = 0 - 2 + 2 = 0$\n\n$z_3 = -3x_1 + 3x_2 + (-1) = -6 + 3 - 1 = -4$\n\n$y = \\max(z_1, z_2, z_3) = \\max(3, 0, -4) = 3$"
